{"tid":1323332,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"雪莉「深夜秀舌技」迷濛眼神片曝光　雙層黑眼圈掉到臉頰！","createTime":"2019-07-16T08:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T08:23:26.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5eeece690b1869ecc80ed0bd0df676362bd9ac","tid":1323332,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:06:52.000Z","msg":"南韓女星雪莉（Sulli，本名：崔真理）原是女團f(x)一員，2015年正式退出，她事後曾透露，因為發現當偶像感覺像是「穿上了不適合自己的衣服」，所以決定退團。雪莉脫掉偶像的衣服後大膽做自己，她15日深夜上傳「舌技影片」，就連素顏的超深黑眼圈也成為亮點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4217/d4217636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4217%2Fd4217636.jpg&h=944b8baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪莉長相甜美，不當偶像後相當做自己。（圖／翻攝自雪莉IG）<br />\n<br />\n雪莉15日深夜IG影片，跟粉絲分享她用舌頭將櫻桃梗打結的絕技。只見雪莉將櫻桃梗放入口中，不斷快速攪動和撥弄舌頭，接著櫻桃梗就在口中變成一個結。雪莉也在貼文表示，自己是第一次挑戰就成功。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4238/d4238314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4238%2Fd4238314.jpg&h=a2245d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪莉用舌頭將櫻桃梗打結，就厚重的黑眼圈嚇壞粉絲。（圖／翻攝自雪莉IG）<br />\n<br />\n不過雪莉疑似沒有上底妝，深深的雙層黑眼圈看來相當駭人，配上她吐舌的迷濛表情，再度讓部分粉絲看了擔心的表示：「妳到底怎麼了？」不過也有人認為，這樣的雪莉很真實，向粉絲分享新技能的行為也非常可愛。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bz8HuQzBIWv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBz8HuQzBIWv%2F&d=FVRAyOQFEUVrsg2I2pbTeR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=4bbf778f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBz8HuQzBIWv%2F&h=0b7555d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bz8HuQzBIWv/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/pl5fu25.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fpl5fu25.gif&h=649258de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d1223c88a7a2d51ef5a2961a848f8558b721e69","tid":1323332,"uid":251836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"653084acfe8a9359e77831e1c140b3534e424b42","tid":1323332,"uid":3405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:22:46.000Z","msg":"癲雞"},{"pid":"abd05461915d963a70fe2c9b7beaa4ebf5c4d2cd","tid":1323332,"uid":257516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"勇武巴絲請入<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}